{"tid":1597883,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[文宣行動]既然大家都唔敢出麻包袋 仲有一招","createTime":"2019-09-27T07:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T07:24:13.000Z","uid":28970,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0aeecf52f80be915740f079b43eed3ad660d19af","tid":1597883,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:01:28.000Z","msg":"大家仲記唔記得大埔隻抽王🍌🍬<br />\n當時班畜牲幾撚驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />果時大家都未用強力膠<br />\n依大家都痴啲柒頭喺地下<br />\n不如試下痴老豆搵仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n嗱入面就好多野嘅 啲人點貼我就唔知啦<br />\n為左表揚班畜牲咁落力一定要公開比人睇<br />\n等有啲冇用TG嘅人都可以知道佢地嘅英勇事蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n打頭陣一定係🍌🍬沙蛇 奠柏林 之後就係指揮官<br />\n再黎梗係1600果幾部錄音機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇下你地得閒啲定我地得閒啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真係諗起都興奮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMon post 狗 係咪好撚驚？ <br />\n我好撚想睇你班柒頭成群結隊出黎撕紙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dmZTF15.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdmZTF15.jpg&h=f0f8ec6e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dtypNG7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdtypNG7.jpg&h=48cb48d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQekk2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQekk2a.jpg&h=4980a338&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oocqw8X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foocqw8X.jpg&h=c1aba7ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N7DM02s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN7DM02s.jpg&h=c1c4d9a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/742U9V5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F742U9V5.gif&h=9ccf49b7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3407f3d9bf40231cd475d1afcd617aea1c5000cf","tid":1597883,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:03:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c627a272694e6409fd620c6760682c14d239b62f","tid":1597883,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21bd745491e5973036106662db8bb9adb94eedcb","tid":1597883,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/biggrin.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />表揚"},{"pid":"045ea655b994556474ff454472b13d721cb4164f","tid":1597883,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97b962885da8fe1fb12bbcb119ad40ba3013f95","tid":1597883,"uid":28970,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:04:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nr8dF4B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnr8dF4B.jpg&h=b1b92157&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd92705d406eb9610dc0b7526c5b52c61dd4b83f","tid":1597883,"uid":259993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33f734022c4d8d49b25c3ba1a0a8d403b4257569","tid":1597883,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:05:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2aac5cbcc047675c4a71f7bde80d76cff1c91c7","tid":1597883,"uid":28970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T07:06:42.000Z","msg":"大家比啲反應 精神啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.